Company Overview of Matterhorn Capital Management LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of December 21, 2016, Matterhorn Capital Management LLC was acquired by Avalon Advisors, LLC. Matterhorn Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations and other businesses, state and municipal government entities, and other investment advisors. It manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of across the globe. For its equity investments, it primarily invests in value and growth stocks of all-cap...
As of December 21, 2016, Matterhorn Capital Management LLC was acquired by Avalon Advisors, LLC. Matterhorn Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations and other businesses, state and municipal government entities, and other investment advisors. It manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of across the globe. For its equity investments, it primarily invests in value and growth stocks of all-cap companies employing a long only strategy. The firm employs a quantitative analysis combining qualitative and fundamental analysis with a bottom-up and top-down approach to make its investments. For its fixed income investments, it invests in taxable and non-taxable portfolios. The firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against Russell 3000 and MSCI AC World Index. Matterhorn Capital Management was founded in February 2005 and is based in San Antonio, Texas.
Detailed Description


